\u8220?We haven\u8217?t even mastered controlled nuclear fusion. Sending a ten-thousand-ton warship to five percent of the speed of light? Ten thousand times faster than the truck-sized spacecraft humanity has today? It\u8217?s not even science fiction. It\u8217?s fantasy!\u8221?\par\pard\plain\hyphpar}{	
