He stood on the ice, his teeth chattering in the cold, a cold that seemed to come not from the lake water or icy wind, but from a direct transmission from outer space. He kept his head down, knowing that from this moment on, the stars were not like they once were. He didn\u8217?t dare look up. As Rey Diaz feared the sun, Luo Ji had acquired a severe phobia of the stars. He bowed his head, and through chattering teeth, said to himself:\par\pard\plain\hyphpar}{	
\u8220?Wallfacer Luo Ji, I am your Wallbreaker.\u8221?\par\pard\plain\hyphpar}{	
